f=Governance/sentinel/logical/book-requirements.md · p=Logical artifacts Python scripts `Shared OS/logical/` (playbook §13.5) sentinel imports. Sentinel owns dedicated script audit sampling inherits cross-agent scripts. file file folder. · h2:Sentinel-Specific Scripts (Shared OS/logical/)=\| # \| Script \| Source \| Route \| Domain \| · h2:Sentinel-Specific Scripts (Shared OS/logical/)=\|---\|--------\|--------\|-------\|--------\| · h2:Sentinel-Specific Scripts (Shared OS/logical/)=\| 1 \| `audit_sampling.py` \| AICPA, *AU-C Section 530: Audit Sampling* (SAS No. 122, amended by SAS No. 142, effective 2022). Publicly available at aicpa.org. \| A \| Attributes sample size, discovery sampling, coverage quantification, stratification, sweep coverage reporting \| · h2:Inherited Scripts (Shared OS/logical/ imported, copied)=\| Script \| Why Sentinel Needs It \| · h2:Inherited Scripts (Shared OS/logical/ imported, copied)=\|--------\|-------------------\| · h2:Inherited Scripts (Shared OS/logical/ imported, copied)=\| `signal_detection.py` \| Control charts (Western Electric rules), two-sample tests, chi-square — anomaly detection for drift-curve readings (sentinel's #2 gap) \| · h2:Inherited Scripts (Shared OS/logical/ imported, copied)=\| `governance_gate.py` \| OECD disclosure standards and sustainability oversight — shared with board \| · h2:Inherited Scripts (Shared OS/logical/ imported, copied)=\| `planning_fallacy.py` \| Calibration for monitoring frequency decisions \| · fc=\| Previously Flagged (0.6) \| Status \| Script \| · fc=\|--------------------------\|--------\|--------\| · fc=\| Sampling: "breadth and regularity" heuristic → not quantifiable \| ✅ Cleared \| `audit_sampling.py` (attributes_sample_size, discovery_sample_size, discovery_coverage_statement) \| · fc=\| Coverage claims: "we looked at a lot" → no confidence level \| ✅ Cleared \| `audit_sampling.py` (sweep_coverage_report — per-domain confidence-quantified upper bounds) \| · fc=\| Anomaly detection: trend vs noise not statistically grounded \| ✅ Cleared \| `signal_detection.py` (Western Electric rules, detect_metric_drift, classify_metric_change) \| · fc=\| Constitution watch: sampling scope not methodologically grounded \| ✅ Cleared \| `audit_sampling.py` (stratified_sample_size with risk weighting) \| · h2:Skills → Script Mapping=**constitution-watch** imports `audit_sampling.py` (sweep_coverage_report, stratified_sample_size) `signal_detection.py` (detect_metric_drift), **gate-bypass-detection** imports `audit_sampling.py` (discovery_sample_size, discovery_coverage_statement) `signal_detection.py` (classify_metric_change), **audit-trail-design** imports `audit_sampling.py` (attributes_sample_size control testing)